articles.description: Applied Mathmatics/Statistics and Economics Double Major at Macalester College
articles.contents: Picture of Nicholas DiGreetings, welcome to my portfolio! I am a double major in Economics and Applied Math/Statistics at Macalester college. I am particularly interested in Econometrics and Probability/Statistics theory. Outside of school, I enjoy going to the gym, reading, and skiing!
